18 consecutive months</strong>. To qualify for a subsequent period of allowances, you must again have worked full-time or part-time for at least 3 months.</p><p>The end date of the insurance policy does not affect the period of relief. These are two separate terms. As long as the insurance term runs (maximum 10 years), you can apply for the allowance, but it is perfectly possible that you will still receive the monthly allowance when the end date of the policy has passed, as long as the conditions are met.</p>"},"@type":"FinancieelVoordeel","order":0}],"creatie":"2009-08-25T08:22:36Z","laatstGewijzigd":"2023-11-14T15:46:50Z","laatstOntvangen":"2024-07-03T06:20:09.622738606Z","productnummer":"185","gearchiveerd":false,"publicatieLink":{"naam":{"en":"See also on vlaanderen.be","nl-BE-x-formal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","en-x-generated":"<p>Flemish Housing Fund<br>Department of Insurance Guaranteed Housing<br>Ieperlaan 41<br>1000 Brussels</p><p>telephone: 02 548 92 39 (available every morning between 8.30 a.m. and 12 noon, except Thursday)<br>e-mail: <a href=\"mailto:vgw@vlaamswoningfonds.be\">vgw@vlaamswoningfonds.be</a></p>","nl":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be"},"url":"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/Product/4767a308-a18f-4533-8381-7cb1d99a755a"},"metadata":{"uJeVersie":"35.4.0","generatedFormeleFields":false,"generatedInformeleFields":true},"@id":"https://ipdc.tni-vlaanderen.be/id/instantiesnapshot/a20c72ad-1972-4d72-8c64-fdcb7fd4fa33","@type":"InstantieSnapshot","isVersionOf":"https://ipdc.tni-vlaanderen.be/id/instantie/88f01834-aece-4d6a-a846-a7f67cd60ac7"},{"id":"dbe114dc-5d4d-4a7f-bbe9-acbc95e0eeea","generatedAtTime":"2024-07-03T06:20:09.025438Z","bevoegdBestuursniveaus":["Vlaams"],"uitvoerendBestuursniveaus":["Vlaams"],"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Huurwaarborglening van het Vlaams Woningfonds","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Huurwaarborglening van het Vlaams Woningfonds","nl":"Huurwaarborglening van het Vlaams 